        (∃ i j H x, of (⟨j, f i j H x⟩ : Σi, G i) - of ⟨i, x⟩ = a) ∨
          (∃ i, of (⟨i, 1⟩ : Σi, G i) - 1 = a) ∨
            (∃ i x y, of (⟨i, x + y⟩ : Σi, G i) - (of ⟨i, x⟩ + of ⟨i, y⟩) = a) ∨
              ∃ i x y, of (⟨i, x * y⟩ : Σi, G i) - of ⟨i, x⟩ * of ⟨i, y⟩ = a }
